hopobject.body: Could I ask who's calling? foredi eceran surabaya Classically trained as a materials scientist I worked as an engineer for years before adopting a career in media. In 2007 I joined AOL's Gadling as an airline writer. That group led me into an editorial role, and I managed the site through the merger with the Huffington Post Media Group. Now, I contribute to a variety of publications including Forbes, The Economist and Lonely Planet and live in Chicago. Follow me on twitter at @grantkmartin
